"Wallace": "I see... This is a pretty nice view too."
"Oh don't get me wrong, I don't have any kind of emotional attachment to this place or anything."
"I've heard about it from other ARKS that made the climb, and I was thinking about going myself..."
"But we're perpetually short on people over here, so I just never had the time to."
"And then I suddenly remembered I had always wanted to... Ah, but this is good enough for me. Thanks."
"Thanks for the image data. Sorry for making you run around everywhere."
"Let me make it up to you someday. Take care, now."
